Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.11,0:00:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, could I borrow a rag?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A rag right?\N- What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for a rag
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I wipe it for you?\N- No it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For Samu to have commited suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hand me some tissue as well
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:37.12,Samu Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)\pos(536.444,436)\frz17.35}Kimu no Koto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did the driver say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister was staggering towards the truck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he honked the car horn and stepped on the brakes as quickly as he could,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,she didn't stop, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She was out to buy something right?\N- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:00:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate?\N- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Apollo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}Takenoko no Sato{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was {\i1}Kinoko no Yama{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Choco Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was milk chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was milk chocolate after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about it being a suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here\N- Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you're driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She just doesn't drink alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd excuse me for a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For it to have been a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she bought chocolate for comfort..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happens to people with dependence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I don't know on Samu's case but,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing that you must quit something but you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an addiction to drinking alcohol after all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only 10 minutes left, please get ready on standby\N- Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimu? Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll be going now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been easily nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Without knowing it, I couldn't stand on stage while sober
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,having this piling anxiety of not being able to sell well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I go straight to the bar after work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can forget everything if I drink after all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Refill please
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the last orders for drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then another 3 of the one I had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,3 High balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As the number of alcohol increased,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so did the number of things I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a time I found the button for calling the clerk at the bar in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There has also been a time I was sleeping with a red cone from a construction site.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a missing part spotted on the bronze statue of a girl smelling a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The concerned locals have began to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a report from the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here at the place where the statue is found, Tsujigaoka Danchi shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As pointed out by my right hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the shopping district's symbol that has grown to be loved by the community, the bronze statue of a girl holding a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, the flower that the girl is supposed to be holding
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,has been broken off and stolen by a cold-hearted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As stated by the woman in charge of cleaning the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"When I was cleaning the statue, I noticed the flower was gone,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"I couldn't find the broken flower anywhere either while cleaning nearby."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So right here, we have the Shopping District's Promotional Association's head, Karasawa-san, to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, please let us hear your feelings about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the shopping district's symbol after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it is important and cherished by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the people of the shopping district and its locals
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,are furious at this cold-hearted person's prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The next station is Higashino
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit is at your left
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful of leaving things behind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That flower will go around and be seen by many people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and it will be back to where it belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I just got it from a fan awhile ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh~ I want to see what's inside
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was told to take a look at it once I'm home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why~ Just show me\N- I said no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning that I go here, I always look at it thinking it was cute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a source of encouragement for me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For this to suddenly happen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so unfortunate, and looking at it now, it's pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hope it is returned soon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning\N- Morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't forgive people like this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone took the bronze statue's flower
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The statue itself has no damage besides the missing flower
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time this has happened
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The town is currently discussing strengthening security via installing security cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job\N- Great job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the thing in the tv?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't much people today either
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lie, that it was given by a fan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...I drank too much so I don't recall doing it though
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You drank that much huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarassing, so don't tell the others okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go put it back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put it back to where it was, there will be no problems right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be found out if we do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will be shocked if it suddenly returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you we can't!\N- It'll be fine. Let's go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu was really a troublesome person
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(661.332,87.11)}Samu! Wait a minute!\N-It'll be fine I'm telling you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not minding the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't mind other people's situation and feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In the case she didn't get to answer her phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,she's the type to keep on calling back until you answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just looking at this famous statue after all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I would right now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our best chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it quick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Did it stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, to commemorate this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We look so ugly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on already let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower sticked somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The incident ended with no problems
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have come to the place where the damaged bronze statue is, Tsujigaoka Danchi shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It originally is a statue of a girl smelling a flower but the once missing flower has now been returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower is faced differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is how it looked before being damaged
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Its original position had the flower facing the girl's face like so, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,right now, as you can see, it is facing the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl is now not smelling the flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it has become the girl that is throwing away a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636.444,65.334)}Was it planned to be this kind of prank all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it better like this though
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(636.444,86.666)}The head of the shopping district's Promotional Association, Karasawa-san, was invited over today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day. So Karasawa-san, so now the girl is-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank all of you for making your way here for Chika
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, that news had a follow-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why is it that the bronze statue,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"the girl who is not smelling the flower", became a buzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,People came to see the statue
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The shopping district which was close to closing came back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The people were able to quickly turn things around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and the situation calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you all called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that name that sounded like a baseball team
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was "Udagawa White Bears"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, it was "Bears"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you guys do again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What work could it have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We sang songs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You sang? What was the chorus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We were idols
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Idols huh?\N- We've already disbanded though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know at all! Were you guys popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I mean I've never seen you after all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about the entertainment world but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty cruel world to those without talent
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, when I was young, I drove a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, I couldn't read maps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit after half a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I often had fights with customers, but it's fun to look back on those memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't drink alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be fine with a little
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are really well-mannered huh~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because of that you guys think I won't suspect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, you've drank too much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get you to sober up outside, come on I'll help you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of idol groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you might think that there is a strong relationship within the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we had to align ourselves everyday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather than a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and not just someone you want to beat either,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with a plastic like superficiality,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it was an unreliable relationship like a sponge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,With no big problems between members,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,nor any touching moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without really meddling on each others lives 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,within ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Samu was the troublesome one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Komiyama-san will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's our ex-manager so he'll probably come right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ones he's handling now is busy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they selling well?\N- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty popular
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Their next live is in Budoukan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Budoukan huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great for them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true\N- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If Samu were alive, she would've probably felt the same
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu really died already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble I caused you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's usually very kind but when the alcohol hits, he can be very hard to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We kind of figured
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fine if I join in the conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Chika around the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister was...a naive person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Naive?\N- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so spoiled at home
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She used to follow me wherever I go when she was young
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go out to play with friends, she makes sure to come along
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I always left the house quietly so that I won't get caught by her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but somehow she senses it and still catches me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already of age at that time so I'd play tricks on her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd follow me even if I teased her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My bicycle was already small and slow even when I'm alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but she'd still pedal with all her strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cute of her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I know I can't top her stamina,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried thinking of a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then actually she often lied
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stupid lies though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "my foot got dislocated, or "my heart stopped".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or "I'll be taken away by a big bird"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite easy to find out though
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it only lies for deception?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh what's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "stopping global warming"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Global warming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she says it and just stopped one day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I've never heard that one before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see\N- I thought that would be the case
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But somehow it's just like Samu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we referred to Chika-san as "Samu"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she was the one who told us to call her that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So she went by as "Samu"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Samu"...was Chika-san not called "Samu" since before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Samu is my nickname
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was called "Samu" before
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Samu" from Osamu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:19:00.57,Samu Title,,0,0,0,,{\frz22.4\fad(900,0)\pos(782.222,439.334)}Samu no Koto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who is this? A different Samu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling of "My sister's happiness is also my own"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll quit from being an idol after all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already here so why don't we take a look?
